# Personal
IMAPAccount Personal
Host imap.migadu.com
User matthew@matthew-kennedy.com
PassCmd "pass matthew@matthew-kennedy.com"
TLSType IMAPS
TLSVersions +1.3

IMAPStore Personal-remote
Account Personal

MaildirStore Personal-local
Path ~/.local/share/mail/personal/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/personal/Inbox
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel Personal
Far :Personal-remote:
Near :Personal-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *

