IMAPAccount icloud
Host imap.mail.me.com
Port 993
User matthew_i_kennedy@icloud.com
# PassCmd "pass mu4e_icloud"
PassCmd "pass outlook_icloud"
TLSType IMAPS
TLSVersions +1.3

IMAPStore icloud-remote
Account icloud

MaildirStore icloud-local
Path ~/.local/share/mail/icloud/
Inbox ~/.local/share/mail/icloud/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel icloud
Far :icloud-remote:
Near :icloud-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "Archive" "Sent Messages" "Drafts" "Deleted Messages" "Junk"
Create Near
Expunge Both
SyncState *
